            <title>[CAMEL-16282] VertxBufferConverter does not handle encoding correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16282</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The changes made for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16270&quot; title=&quot;Vertx Buffer converter should sharable among vertx components and not tied with vertx-web.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CAMEL-16270&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CAMEL-16270&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; revealed an issue in that the VertxBufferConverter is not handling encoding correctly. The issue was masked by some (actually my) incorrect unit tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed the problem on the camel-quarkus side as the platform-http encoding test started failing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
